Third-party data and credits:

- Dictionary data is CC-CEDICT, licensed CC BY-SA 4.0
  (https://cc-cedict.org/ , https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=cc-cedict).
  It is downloaded by scripts/lang/zh/build-dict.mjs and is not redistributed in this
  repository. Any distribution that bundles the generated dictionary file must
  comply with CC BY-SA 4.0.

- The tap-to-define + word-highlighting interaction is inspired by the Zhongwen
  popup-dictionary browser extension (https://github.com/cschiller/zhongwen,
  GPL-2.0). No Zhongwen code is used here; the segmentation and highlighting were
  reimplemented clean-room, so this project remains under the MIT license above.
